%h1 Customer Feedback and Comments
%p
  We're here to help! And we would love to hear what you think of our product. If you would like to give us any feedback, or would like to make any feature requests, please don't hesitate to contact us using the form below. Thank you for your support!
%br
  = simple_form_for(@suggestion) do |f|
    = f.error_notification
    .form-inputs
      = f.input :subject
      = f.input :suggestion
    = f.button :submit, class: 'btn btn-primary'
  %p
    If you have any Support related issue, please use the #{link_to "Contact Us", contact_us_path} page instead.
  Head back to the #{link_to 'Home page.', root_path}, but please come back soon!
  %br
    Or to login again, #{link_to 'click here', new_user_session_path}